Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12點鐘方向，敵方AS一架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是M9嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法確認！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要落單！一起包夾它吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作太快了，無法鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在右邊！右邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點，敵人只有一架而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#07 BOY MEETS GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀色的AS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲得真漂亮，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊佔了上風？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如是平常的戰鬥\n應該算是平分秋色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那架銀色的AS不是普通貨色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它還留有一招神秘的絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的子彈可是在空中被彈開了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它到底耍了什麼把戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對，不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是技術，是科技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人擁有它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的機體卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小要？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會輸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是散彈地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是爆炸式反應裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是一道看不見的牆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到那樣的衝擊還…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R，剛才那是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主系統開機精靈執行中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統開啟還要20秒\n什麼？你在做什麼？R
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未爆彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再來一發
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver初始化結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法回答，請繼續戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我，R！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那時機體明明就被\n打得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎…能夠了解…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要，不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不知道使用的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強烈的防衛衝動讓…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要，振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得把…提示…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提示？是什麼提示？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老是讓別人救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次要由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類相位…干涉….
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會認輸呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要，妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊器借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快點告訴他才行，快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次你抵擋得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良，聽得見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千鳥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遇到的敵人裝有特別的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它…它是能將駕駛的攻擊衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉變成物理力量的機械
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千…千鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還有，雖然我不知理由為何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你的AS也裝有那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也裝有λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才有產生\n想要保護自己的念頭對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝置便對此產生了反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心中的強烈想像會化為實體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像變成實體？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種武器怎麼可能存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手剛才本來想把你炸燬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他卻沒辦法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至還能反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中強烈的想著\n要把對手打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中在一瞬間！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們保護著傾聽者(Whispered)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算擁有這東西\n也沒什麼好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神啊，集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才就一直在做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有產生力場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這樣用才對！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算這樣一直逃下去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不知道\n這裝置的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該來做個了斷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好，相良
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是集中力！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸後，在吐氣的瞬間\n像是把精神注入子彈般的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖然是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想像一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸的話，我的衣服就會被剝光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體被徹底的玩弄之後\n最後會被殺掉的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像一下那幅光景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不願意看到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會很火嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就是打算這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能允許那種事情發生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，把槍對準那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於豁出去了是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人失望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，把眼睛閉上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你腦中想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下會去把那傢伙痛毆一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能在敵人面前閉上眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後吸一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把想像…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良，你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是世界上最不適合\n用來搬運傷患的交通工具了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再發牢騷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺如何？千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，比之前好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過剛才我說了什麼，我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧？千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後會很恐怖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要，是海喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還附帶了盛大的送行隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛7號，朝直線跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介，機會只有一次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從岬的尖端直接起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛7號回收
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從第四艙門收納…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四艙門開始閉鎖，還需兩秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉鎖完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右滿舵，方向2-0-5，最大戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右滿舵，方向2-0-5，最大戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慘哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龍怎樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想親眼目睹那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有話想說是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,λ-Driver究竟是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校，我也懂一些基本的物理學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒聽說過\n能夠操控那種力量的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個世代或許沒什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的武器科技相當的異常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ECS、還是這潛艦的推進系統
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個都太過於先進了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種如科幻作品般的機器人武器\n竟然能稱霸於戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有感覺過這很不自然嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…今天第一次這麼想過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從以前就有這個疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西是不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，它卻實際的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支撐著AS等現行武器的技術體系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑科技\N到底是誰發明的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說它到底是從哪裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是像千鳥那樣的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為傾聽者(Whispered)的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不能由我口中說出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你可以將之放在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，有關千鳥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報部已經放出了假情報
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謊稱雖然九龍他們調查過千鳥要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她卻不是傾聽者(Whispered)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她暫時應該是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，還是有必要加個保險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保險？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒過來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介沒事，不需要為他操心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？妳又是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是東京的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳睡了兩天了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們送妳過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是宗介的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為時間不多，我就簡潔的說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好，千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在那基地被注射藥物之後\n就這樣失去了意識
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再醒來時\n就已經在這個醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之間發生的事情\n妳什麼也不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部把它忘光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們究竟是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是秘銀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊潰恐怖組織或是破壞毒品工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是維護世界正義的軍隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘銀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是名字的話\n我想在日本應該也有人聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，如果不想惹來麻煩\n妳就說什麼都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這種說法裝蒜到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得跟妳道謝才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道謝？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳救了我的兩個部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我並沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有妳在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介跟克魯茲一定活不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳或許比我們還要堅強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經去執行其他任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有沒有留言？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給妳的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有特別交代耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，我真的很擔心妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後\n我們在福岡機場被趕下了運輸機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後救援部隊就消失不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好像跟聯合國\n沒有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…\n人家不知道小要到哪裡去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過剛才學校好像接到了\n醫院的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說妳被送到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那個時候應該代替妳被抓走的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下啦，真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是病人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，雖說是輕微撞傷\n還是要好好靜養才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，要好好照顧我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要感謝那些救援部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，雖然修學旅行泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留得青山在不怕沒柴燒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊\n留得青山在不怕沒柴燒….
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相…相良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣問我，我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來探病的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物也準備好了，妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是保險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間暫時…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了喔，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，這些煙是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，資料…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生火災了…\n文字處理機…文字處理機…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用了煙霧彈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳說要我下一點工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把視野完全遮敝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但能在不被看到臉的情況下\n安全的奪取到影印紙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會對我們起嫌…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個大白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這戰爭癡呆的陰沉男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎麼搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就連紙都一起毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就一點意義都沒有了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾乾的話我想應該還可以用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要辯解！
